{
  "uid": "gap-scorecard",
  "title": "Gap Scorecard — distance to Netflix-lite",
  "tags": ["streamflix", "gap"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## How far is the backend from a lite Netflix-like platform?\nEach tile shows the **measured** value under load; **green = meeting the target SLO**, **red = gap remains**. Targets: read p95 < 200ms, write p95 < 250ms, reco p95 < 150ms, error rate < 0.1%, throughput ~500 events/sec, DB pool < 80%."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Write p95 (ms) — target < 250",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{application=\"video-service\", method=\"POST\", uri=~\"/api/videos/.+/(watch|view|rate|like)\"}[1m])) by (le)) * 1000"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 250 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Read p95 (ms) — target < 200",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{application=\"video-service\", method=\"GET\"}[1m])) by (le)) * 1000"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 200 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Recommendation p95 (ms) — target < 150",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 3 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{application=\"recommendation-service\", method=\"GET\"}[1m])) by (le)) * 1000"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 150 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "OLTP throughput (accepted writes/sec) — target ~500",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{application=\"video-service\", status=\"202\"}[1m]))"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "red", "value": null },
            { "color": "green", "value": 475 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error rate — target < 0.1%",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{outcome=~\"SERVER_ERROR|CLIENT_ERROR\"}[1m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count[1m])), 1)"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 0.001 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "DB pool utilization (video-service) — target < 80%",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max(hikaricp_connections_active{application=\"video-service\"}) / max(hikaricp_connections_max{application=\"video-service\"})"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "green", "value": null },
            { "color": "red", "value": 0.8 }
          ] }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } }
    }
  ]
}
